xcellent change from the various chutneys and sauces around. The mint gives it that distinctive English, summery flavour, while the earthy beetroot provides a glorious colour. It’s lovely with roast meats, cold meats and in sandwiches."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h","1 total recipe"]}